FoH is on my server and definitely has been working that zone over. A /who
all fire never lies, most of them aren't anonymous, and many of my friends
there are pissed because they don't have their keys yet. :) On a slightly
similar note, I wish they had never toned down Siren's Ghetto... Necropolis
is starting to have Sebilis-like populations lately. :(

Sartori<Legion>
